{"tid":1645214,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"庫克為蘋果下架追蹤港警App作辯護","createTime":"2019-10-10T20:36:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-11T18:36:46.000Z","uid":1086,"like":2,"dislike":130,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"8fb941f326d3eba68c25288b446f62dc522bce2d","tid":1645214,"uid":1086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T20:36:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.hkej.com/hkej/images/2019/10/11/2273102_49c407d59e42f41db3efcadd86c908a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.hkej.com%2Fhkej%2Fimages%2F2019%2F10%2F11%2F2273102_49c407d59e42f41db3efcadd86c908a4.png&h=e4377efe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n被指為香港暴力示威者「護航」的地圖應用程式HKmap live，遭到美國蘋果公司下架，行政總裁庫克(Tim Cook)為下架決定辯護。<br />\n<br />\n路透周四引述庫克致函蘋果員工的一封信件，庫克在信中表示，蘋果收到來自香港警方以及蘋果用戶的「可信資料」，指遭下架的應用程式(App)被用作<span style=\"color: red;\">「惡意針對個別警員施暴，以及在沒有警員在場時，使個別市民及財物成為受害對象」</span>。<br />\n<br />\n庫克指出，這款應用程式的使用構成違反香港法律。同樣地，廣泛濫用這款應用程式，也違反蘋果應用商店禁止對個人造成傷害的指引。"},{"pid":"9dc75533a689503c4a5aa732a3c769fea6b3c9d7","tid":1645214,"uid":79117,"like":72,"dislike":0,"score":72,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T20:37:17.000Z","msg":"WeChat下架未？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0428213542fce55d9a32b9538bddb0142da82690","tid":1645214,"uid":9777,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T20:37:44.000Z","msg":"屌你老母gay cook<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0b01253023a75ab4c7bf137692563eadabf98c6","tid":1645214,"uid":3893,"like":39,"dislike":0,"score":39,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T20:37:48.000Z","msg":"個別警員施暴<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />應該全部呀嘛<br />\n收皮啦Tim cook繼續奶共啦"},{"pid":"9a32969008e469f9508db44c636b959ebbc144da","tid":1645214,"uid":129848,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T20:38:44.000Z","msg":"屌你老母聽警隊話咪即係跪囉 仲以為係defend緊自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid"